  We recommend using another libSQL provider such as <a href="https://turso.tech" target="_blank">Turso</a> 
  or self-hosting your own <a href="https://github.com/tursodatabase/libsql/tree/main" target="_blank">libSQL server</a>.
  <ReadMore>
    For more information regarding the sunset of Studio, see 
    <a href="https://astro.build/blog/goodbye-astro-studio/" target="_blank">Astro's 'Goodbye Studio, Hello DB' Blog Post</a>
  </ReadMore>
</Aside>
